      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_09f47cf90a63ba8949fd087286f7501d">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged by accession.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_c8d25a01aeae9f727f3bedc76697c199">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of exhibit programs, posters, supporting materials, and audiotapes documenting exhibits from the Yale Center for British Art.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
